{"data":[{"date":"09:46 20/08","title":"Nh\u1eadn \u0111\u1ecbnh U23 Tri\u1ec1u Ti\u00ean vs U23 Saudi Arabia 16h00 ng\u00e0y 20/8 (ASIAD 2018)","type":"B\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 Anh","img_url":"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/8/20/nhan-dinh-u23-trieu-tien-vs-u23-saudi-arabia-16h00-ngay-208-asiad-2018.jpg","new_desc":"<link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><h2>U23 Tri\u1ec1u Ti\u00ean vs U23 Saudi Arabia l\u00fac 16h00 ng\u00e0y 20/8(V\u00f2ng b\u1ea3ng m\u00f4n b\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 nam Asian 2018): Nh\u1eadn \u0111\u1ecbnh b\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1, \u00fd ki\u1ebfn chuy\u00ean gia, d\u1ef1 \u0111o\u00e1n k\u1ebft qu\u1ea3, ph\u00e2n t\u00edch chuy\u00ean m\u00f4n, c\u00e1c th\u00f4ng tin, th\u1ed1ng k\u00ea b\u00ean l\u1ec1 tr\u01b0\u1edbc tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u.</h2><div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width:100%; text-align: center;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"Nh\u1eadn \u0111\u1ecbnh U23 Tri\u1ec1u Ti\u00ean vs U23 Saudi Arabia 16h00 ng\u00e0y 208 h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" title=\"Nh\u1eadn \u0111\u1ecbnh U23 Tri\u1ec1u Ti\u00ean vs U23 Saudi Arabia 16h00 ng\u00e0y 208 h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/8/20/U23_Saudi_Arabia.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td style=\"text-align: center\">U23 Tri\u1ec1u Ti\u00ean vs U23 Saudi Arabia</td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<br>\r\n<h2 style=\"color: rgb(0, 0, 0); font-family: Arial, Verdana, sans-serif; font-style: normal; font-variant-ligatures: normal; font-variant-caps: normal; letter-spacing: normal; orphans: 2; text-align: start; text-indent: 0px; text-transform: none; white-space: normal; widows: 2; word-spacing: 0px; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); text-decoration-style: initial; text-decoration-color: initial;\"><span href=\"https://bongda24h.vn/nhan-dinh-bong-da-c344-p1.html\" target=\"_blank\">Nh\u1eadn \u0111\u1ecbnh b\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1</span><span><span><span><span><span><span><span><span><span><span><span><span><span><span><span><span><span><span><span><span><span><span><span><span><span><span><span><span><span><span><span><span><span><span><span><span><span><span><span><span><span><span><span><span><span><span><span><span><span><span><span><span><span><span><span><span><span><span><span><span> </span></span></span></span>U23 Tri\u1ec1u Ti\u00ean vs U23 Saudi Arabia: 1-2<br>\r\n</span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></h2>\r\nU23 Saudi Arabia \u0111\u00e3 c\u00f3 4 \u0111i\u1ec3m sau 2 l\u01b0\u1ee3t tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea7u ti\u00ean v\u00e0 c\u00e1nh c\u1eeda \u0111i ti\u1ebfp \u0111\u00e3 r\u1ea5t r\u1ed9ng m\u1edf \u0111\u1ed1i v\u1edbi h\u1ecd. Ch\u1ec9 c\u1ea7n m\u1ed9t tr\u1eadn h\u00f2a \u1edf l\u01b0\u1ee3t tr\u1eadn cu\u1ed1i n\u00e0y c\u0169ng \u0111\u1ee7 \u0111\u1ec3 U23 Saudi Arabia v\u00e0o v\u00f2n 1/8, tuy nhi\u00ean \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng n\u00e0y mong mu\u1ed1n nhi\u1ec1u h\u01a1n th\u1ebf.<br>\r\n<br>\r\nU23 Tri\u1ec1u Ti\u00ean h\u00f2a U23 Myanmar \u1edf tr\u1eadn m\u1edf m\u00e0n v\u00e0 \u0111\u1ed5 g\u1ee5c tr\u01b0\u1edbc s\u1ee9c m\u1ea1nh c\u1ee7a U23 Iran (thua 0-3) \u1edf l\u01b0\u1ee3t tr\u1eadn th\u1ee9 2 n\u00ean \u0111\u00e1nh gi\u00e1 kh\u00e1ch quan, c\u01a1 h\u1ed9i ki\u1ebfm v\u00e9 v\u00e0o v\u00f2ng sau c\u1ee7a U23 Tri\u1ec1u Ti\u00ean th\u1ef1c s\u1ef1 ch\u1ec9 c\u00f2n n\u1eb1m tr\u00ean l\u00fd thuy\u1ebft d\u00f9 r\u1eb1ng n\u1ebfu th\u1eafng tr\u1eadn n\u00e0y, m\u1ecdi th\u1ee9 s\u1ebd l\u1ea1i r\u1ed9ng m\u1edf song U23 Saudi Arabia r\u00f5 r\u00e0ng tr\u1ed9i h\u01a1n.<br>\r\n<br>\r\nChuy\u00ean gia \u0111ang c\u00f3 xu h\u01b0\u1edbng quay l\u01b0ng l\u1ea1i v\u1edbi U23 Tri\u1ec1u Ti\u00ean. T\u00ednh t\u1eeb th\u00e1ng 1 cho t\u1edbi nay, h\u1ecd \u0111\u00e3 kh\u00f4ng th\u1eafng 8 tr\u1eadn li\u00ean ti\u1ebfp. V\u1edbi th\u1ed1ng k\u00ea n\u00e0y vi\u1ec7c g\u1eedi g\u1eafm hy v\u1ecdng v\u00e0o U23 Tri\u1ec1u Ti\u00ean th\u1ef1c s\u1ef1 qu\u00e1 m\u1ea1o hi\u1ec3m.<br>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width:100%; text-align: center;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"Bang F ASIAD\" title=\"B\u1ea3ng F ASIAD\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/8/19/BXH-bang-F-truoc-luot-dau-cuoi.png\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td style=\"text-align: center\">\u00a0</td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<br></div><advbottom>","new_url":"","id":"2569","checkdouble":"194877"},{"date":"10:31 20/08","title":"Anthony Martial b\u1ecb ch\u1ec9 tr\u00edch d\u1eef d\u1ed9i sau tr\u1eadn thua Brighton","type":"B\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 Anh","img_url":"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/8/20/anthony-martial-bi-chi-trich-du-doi-sau-tran-thua-brighton.jpg","new_desc":"<link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><h2>Anthony Martial g\u00e2y th\u1ea5t v\u1ecdng v\u00e0 b\u1ecb c\u1ef1u HLV tuy\u1ec3n Anh Sam Allardyce ch\u1ec9 tr\u00edch d\u1eef d\u1ed9i sau m\u00e0n tr\u00ecnh di\u1ec5n th\u1ea3m h\u1ea1i tr\u01b0\u1edbc Brighton, Big Sam kh\u1eb3ng \u0111\u1ecbnh c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 ng\u01b0\u1eddi Ph\u00e1p l\u00e0 m\u1ed9t trong nh\u1eefng l\u00fd do khi\u1ebfn Qu\u1ef7 \u0111\u1ecf tr\u1eafng tay tr\u00ean s\u00e2n Falmer.\r\n</h2><h2 style=\"text-align: justify;\">Martial ch\u01a1i m\u1edd nh\u1ea1t tr\u01b0\u1edbc Brighton</h2>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nTrong chuy\u1ebfn du \u0111\u1ea5u tr\u00ean \u0111\u1ea5t M\u1ef9, ti\u1ec1n \u0111\u1ea1o Anthony Martial \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c cho l\u00e0 c\u00f3 m\u00e2u thu\u1eabn v\u1edbi HLV Jose Mourinho. C\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 ng\u01b0\u1eddi Ph\u00e1p \u0111\u00f2i ra \u0111i nh\u01b0ng \u00f4ng th\u1ea7y ng\u01b0\u1eddi B\u1ed3 kh\u00f4ng cho ph\u00e9p.<br>\r\n\u00a0</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width: 100%;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"Big Sam ch\u1ec9 tr\u00edch Anthony Martial g\u00e2y th\u1ea5t v\u1ecdng tr\u01b0\u1edbc Brighton h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" title=\"Big Sam ch\u1ec9 tr\u00edch Anthony Martial g\u00e2y th\u1ea5t v\u1ecdng tr\u01b0\u1edbc Brighton h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/8/20/anthony-martial-bi-chi-trich-du-doi-sau-tran-thua-brighton.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td>\r\n            <h3>Martial ch\u01a1i m\u1edd nh\u1ea1t tr\u01b0\u1edbc Brighton</h3>\r\n            </td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<br>\r\n\u1ede v\u00f2ng 1 g\u1eb7p Leicester, Martial \u0111\u00e3 kh\u00f4ng c\u00f3 c\u01a1 h\u1ed9i \u0111\u00e1 ch\u00ednh. Trong chuy\u1ebfn l\u00e0m kh\u00e1ch tr\u00ean s\u00e2n Falmer c\u1ee7a Brighton, <span href=\"https://bongda24h.vn/bong-da-anh/mourinho-noi-gi-ve-chan-thuong-cua-alexis-sanchez-172-194874.html\" target=\"_blank\">Sanchez ch\u1ea5n th\u01b0\u01a1ng</span> bu\u1ed9c Mourinho ph\u1ea3i trao c\u01a1 h\u1ed9i \u0111\u00e1 ch\u00ednh cho Martial.\u00a0</div>\r\n</div><mobileadv><link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\n\u0110\u00e2y l\u00e0 c\u01a1 h\u1ed9i r\u1ea5t t\u1ed1t \u0111\u1ec3 c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 23 tu\u1ed5i kh\u1eb3ng \u0111\u1ecbnh m\u00ecnh, song r\u1ea5t ti\u1ebfc c\u1ef1u sao Monaco ch\u1ec9 \u0111em l\u1ea1i s\u1ef1 th\u1ea5t v\u1ecdng.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nMartial ch\u01a1i m\u1edd nh\u1ea1t tr\u01b0\u1edbc Brighton, d\u00f9 thi \u0111\u1ea5u \u1edf v\u1ecb tr\u00ed ti\u1ec1n \u0111\u1ea1o c\u00e1nh tr\u00e1i s\u1edf tr\u01b0\u1eddng trong s\u01a1 \u0111\u1ed3 4-3-3, song c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 ng\u01b0\u1eddi Ph\u00e1p kh\u00f4ng c\u00f3 m\u1ed9t c\u00fa d\u1ee9t\u00a0\u0111i\u1ec3m tr\u00fang \u0111\u00edch n\u00e0o, anh c\u0169ng kh\u00f4ng t\u1ea1o ra c\u01a1 h\u1ed9i n\u00e0o cho c\u00e1c \u0111\u1ed3ng \u0111\u1ed9i.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nNh\u1eefng ph\u00fat c\u00f3 m\u1eb7t tr\u00ean s\u00e2n, Martial ch\u1ec9 tung ra duy nh\u1ea5t m\u1ed9t c\u00fa d\u1ee9t \u0111i\u1ec3m kh\u00f4ng tr\u00fang \u0111\u00edch. V\u1edbi m\u00e0n tr\u00ecnh di\u1ec5n th\u1ea5t v\u1ecdng c\u1ee7a m\u00ecnh anh b\u1ecb thay ra \u1edf ph\u00fat 59, sau tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u Mourinho kh\u00f4ng h\u00e0i l\u00f2ng v\u1edbi phong \u0111\u1ed9 c\u1ee7a c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 sinh n\u0103m 1995.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">\u00a0</div>\r\n<h2>Sam Allardyce ch\u1ec9 tr\u00edch Martial</h2>\r\n<h2>\u00a0</h2>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">Anthony Martial g\u00e2y th\u1ea5t v\u1ecdng v\u00e0 b\u1ecb c\u1ef1u HLV tuy\u1ec3n Anh Sam Allardyce ch\u1ec9 tr\u00edch d\u1eef d\u1ed9i sau m\u00e0n tr\u00ecnh di\u1ec5n th\u1ea3m h\u1ea1i tr\u01b0\u1edbc Brighton, Big Sam kh\u1eb3ng \u0111\u1ecbnh c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 ng\u01b0\u1eddi Ph\u00e1p l\u00e0 m\u1ed9t trong nh\u1eefng l\u00fd do khi\u1ebfn Qu\u1ef7 \u0111\u1ecf tr\u1eafng tay tr\u00ean s\u00e2n Falmer.<br>\r\n\u00a0</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width: 100%;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"Martial bi chi trich sau tran thua Brighton\" title=\"Martial b\u1ecb ch\u1ec9 tr\u00edch sau tr\u1eadn thua Brighton\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/8/20/martial-2.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td>\r\n            <h3>Martial b\u1ecb ch\u1ec9 tr\u00edch sau tr\u1eadn thua Brighton</h3>\r\n            </td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<br>\r\n\u201cC\u1eadu \u1ea5y ch\u01a1i kh\u00f4ng t\u1ed1t tr\u01b0\u1edbc Brighton, c\u1eadu \u1ea5y kh\u00f4ng t\u1ef1 t\u1ea1o ra nh\u1eefng c\u01a1 h\u1ed9i v\u00e0 c\u0169ng kh\u00f4ng ph\u1ed1i h\u1ee3p t\u1ed1t v\u1edbi c\u00e1c \u0111\u1ed3ng \u0111\u1ed9i. Martial l\u00e0 c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 ch\u01a1i th\u1ea5t v\u1ecdng nh\u1ea5t c\u1ee7a M.U \u1edf tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u v\u1edbi Brighton, ch\u00ednh phong \u0111\u1ed9 t\u1ec7 h\u1ea1i c\u1ee7a c\u1eadu \u1ea5y khi\u1ebfn M.U ph\u1ea3i nh\u1eadn th\u1ea5t b\u1ea1i\u201d.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\n\u201cMartial t\u1eebng \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c \u0111\u00e1nh gi\u00e1 c\u00f3 ti\u1ec1m n\u0103ng l\u1edbn, c\u1eadu \u1ea5y t\u1eebng \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c so s\u00e1nh v\u1edbi Sterling v\u00e0 Sane. Tuy nhi\u00ean, \u1edf th\u1eddi \u0111i\u1ec3m hi\u1ec7n t\u1ea1i c\u1eadu \u1ea5y \u0111\u00e3 k\u00e9m h\u01a1n r\u1ea5t nhi\u1ec1u khi \u0111\u1eb7t b\u00ean c\u1ea1nh b\u1ed9 \u0111\u00f4i c\u1ee7a Man City, c\u1eadu \u1ea5y kh\u00f4ng x\u1ee9ng \u0111\u00e1ng v\u1edbi s\u1ed1 ti\u1ec1n m\u00e0 M.U b\u1ecf ra\u201d.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\n\u201cT\u00f4i kh\u00f4ng hi\u1ec3u t\u1ea1i sao M.U l\u1ea1i kh\u00f4ng b\u00e1n Martial \u1edf H\u00e8 2018, s\u1ebd h\u1ee3p l\u00fd h\u01a1n n\u1ebfu h\u1ecd \u0111\u1ea9y c\u1eadu \u1ea5y ra \u0111i v\u00e0 thu v\u1ec1 m\u1ed9t s\u1ed1 ti\u1ec1n l\u1edbn sau \u0111\u00f3 \u0111\u1ea7u t\u01b0 v\u00e0o nh\u1eefng th\u01b0\u01a1ng v\u1ee5 kh\u00e1c\u201d.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nV\u01b0\u01a1ng Ng\u00e2n (TTVN)</div></div><advbottom>","new_url":"","id":"2568","checkdouble":"194878"},{"date":"10:11 20/08","title":"Scholes \u0111\u1eb7t d\u1ea5u h\u1ecfi v\u1ec1 l\u1eddi nh\u1eadn l\u1ed7i c\u1ee7a Pogba","type":"B\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 Anh","img_url":"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/8/20/scholes-chi-trich-pogba-sau-tran-thua-brighton.jpg","new_desc":"<link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><h2>Gary Neville ph\u00e1t bi\u1ec3u v\u1ec1 M.U. C\u1ef1u danh th\u1ee7 n\u00e0y tin r\u1eb1ng l\u00e3nh \u0111\u1ea1o Qu\u1ef7 \u0111\u1ecf \u0111\u00e3 thi\u1ebfu \u0111i s\u1ef1 h\u1ed7 tr\u1ee3 v\u1edbi HLV Jose Mourinho trong c\u00f4ng t\u00e1c chuy\u1ec3n nh\u01b0\u1ee3ng.</h2><div style=\"text-align: justify;\">\u00a0</div>\r\n<h2>M.U tr\u1ea3 gi\u00e1 v\u00ec chuy\u1ec3n nh\u01b0\u1ee3ng th\u1ea5t b\u1ea1i</h2>\r\n</div><mobileadv><link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nM\u00f9a h\u00e8 n\u00e0y, Man United ch\u1ec9 mang v\u1ec1 3 t\u00e2n binh bao g\u1ed3m ti\u1ec1n v\u1ec7 Fred, h\u1eadu v\u1ec7 c\u00e1nh Diogo Dalot v\u00e0 th\u1ee7 m\u00f4n Lee Grant. Tuy nhi\u00ean, ch\u1ec9 1 trong s\u1ed1 n\u00e0y l\u00e0 Fred v\u1eeba \u00fd HLV Jose Mourinho. Nh\u1eefng Dalot non kinh nghi\u1ec7m hay Grant l\u1edbn tu\u1ed5i \u0111\u1ec1u kh\u00f4ng ph\u1ea3i nh\u1eefng gi\u1ea3i ph\u00e1p t\u1ee9c th\u00ec.<br>\r\n<br>\r\n\u0110\u00e3 xu\u1ea5t hi\u1ec7n nh\u1eefng tin \u0111\u1ed3n v\u1ec1 vi\u1ec7c M.U li\u00ean h\u1ec7 v\u1edbi Toby Alderweireld c\u1ee7a Tottenham v\u00e0 Harry Maguire c\u1ee7a Leicester City. Tuy nhi\u00ean, \u0111\u1ebfn cu\u1ed1i phi\u00ean ch\u1ee3 h\u00e8 2018 d\u00e0nh cho c\u00e1c CLB Premier League, kh\u00f4ng c\u00f3 th\u00eam b\u1ea5t c\u1ee9 ai c\u1eadp b\u1ebfn Old Trafford.<br>\r\n<br>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width:100%; text-align: center;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"Gary Neville ph\u00e1t bi\u1ec3u v\u1ec1 MU v\u00e0 Mourinho h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" title=\"Gary Neville ph\u00e1t bi\u1ec3u v\u1ec1 MU v\u00e0 Mourinho h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/8/20/Gary-Neville-phat-bieu-ve-MU-va-Mourinho-hinh-anh.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td style=\"text-align: center\">M.U \u0111ang c\u00f3 nh\u1eefng k\u1ebft qu\u1ea3 kh\u00f4ng t\u1ed1t</td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<br>\r\nH\u1ec7 qu\u1ea3 l\u00e0 M.U c\u00f3 nh\u1eefng m\u00e0n tr\u00ecnh di\u1ec5n k\u00e9m thuy\u1ebft ph\u1ee5c tr\u00ean s\u00e2n c\u1ecf. T\u1ea1i Premier League, sau chi\u1ebfn th\u1eafng 2-1 ch\u1eadt v\u1eadt tr\u01b0\u1edbc Leicester, h\u1ecd th\u1ea5t th\u1ee7 2-3 tr\u00ean s\u00e2n Brighton \u0111\u1ec3 l\u1ea1i nhi\u1ec1u lo l\u1eafng cho ng\u01b0\u1eddi h\u00e2m m\u1ed9.<br>\r\n\u00a0</div>\r\n<h2>Neville ch\u1ec9 tr\u00edch l\u00e3nh \u0111\u1ea1o M.U</h2>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nC\u1ef1u \u0111\u1ed9i tr\u01b0\u1edfng Gary Neville ph\u00e1t bi\u1ec3u v\u1ec1 M.U. Anh tin r\u1eb1ng Gi\u00e1m \u0111\u1ed1c \u0111i\u1ec1u h\u00e0nh Ed Woodward c\u00f9ng l\u00e3nh \u0111\u1ea1o Qu\u1ef7 \u0111\u1ecf c\u1ea7n h\u1ed7 tr\u1ee3 Mourinho trong mua s\u1eafm n\u1ebfu mu\u1ed1n b\u00f9 \u0111\u1eafp cho nh\u1eefng sai l\u1ea7m c\u1ee7a qu\u00e1 kh\u1ee9 sau khi Alex Ferguson ngh\u1ec9 h\u01b0u v\u00e0o n\u0103m 2013.<br>\r\n<br>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width:100%; text-align: center;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"HLV Mourinho\" title=\"HLV Mourinho\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/8/20/gary-neville-phat-bieu-ve-mu.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td style=\"text-align: center\">\r\n            <h3>Gary Neville ph\u00e1t bi\u1ec3u v\u1ec1 M.U v\u00e0 Mourinho</h3>\r\n            </td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<br>\r\n\u201cMourinho \u0111ang \u1edf m\u00f9a gi\u1ea3i th\u1ee9 3 v\u00e0 t\u00f4i ngh\u0129 \u00f4ng \u1ea5y s\u1ebd c\u1ea3m th\u1ea5y v\u00f4 c\u00f9ng th\u1ea5t v\u1ecdng khi kh\u00f4ng nh\u1eadn \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c h\u1ed7 tr\u1ee3 tr\u00ean th\u1ecb tr\u01b0\u1eddng chuy\u1ec3n nh\u01b0\u1ee3ng\u201d, Neville n\u00f3i tr\u00ean Sky Sports. \u201cB\u1ea1n kh\u00f4ng th\u1ec3 \u0111\u1ec3 m\u1ed9t ng\u00f4i nh\u00e0 v\u1edbi 3/4 l\u00e0 \u0111ang x\u00e2y d\u1ef1ng. B\u1ea1n ph\u1ea3i ho\u00e0n th\u00e0nh n\u00f3 v\u00e0 ho\u00e0n th\u00e0nh vi\u1ec7c x\u00e2y d\u1ef1ng. Sau \u0111\u00f3, b\u1ea1n m\u1edbi c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 ngh\u0129 v\u1ec1 vi\u1ec7c b\u00e1n ho\u1eb7c cho thu\u00ea n\u00f3.\u201d<br>\r\n<br>\r\n\u201cKh\u00f4ng ai nh\u1eadn ng\u00f4i nh\u00e0 \u0111\u00f3 n\u1ebfu n\u00f3 c\u00f2n dang d\u1edf. M.U \u0111\u00e3 g\u1eb7p v\u1ea5n \u0111\u1ec1 tr\u00ean th\u1ecb tr\u01b0\u1eddng chuy\u1ec3n nh\u01b0\u1ee3ng k\u1ec3 t\u1eeb khi Sir Alex Ferguson ngh\u1ec9 h\u01b0u. Nh\u1eefng David Moyes v\u00e0 sau \u0111\u00f3 l\u00e0 Louis van Gaal \u0111\u00e3 chi kh\u00f4ng d\u01b0\u1edbi 700 tri\u1ec7u b\u1ea3ng nh\u01b0ng kh\u00f4ng mang l\u1ea1i gi\u00e1 tr\u1ecb.\u201d<br>\r\n<br>\r\n\u201cMourinho c\u1ea7n \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c \u0111\u1ea7u t\u01b0 th\u00eam. R\u00f5 r\u00e0ng l\u00e0 CLB n\u00ean h\u1ed7 tr\u1ee3 \u00f4ng \u1ea5y. B\u1ea1n kh\u00f4ng th\u1ec3 h\u1ee7y b\u1ecf m\u1ed9t d\u1ef1 \u00e1n khi c\u00f2n \u0111ang trong qu\u00e1 tr\u00ecnh x\u00e2y d\u1ef1ng. Kh\u00f4ng d\u1ec5 d\u00e0ng \u0111\u1ec3 c\u1ea1nh tranh c\u00e1c danh hi\u1ec7u trong t\u00ecnh h\u00ecnh hi\u1ec7n nay.\u201d<br>\r\n<strong><br>\r\nXem th\u00eam m\u1ed9t s\u1ed1 b\u00e0i vi\u1ebft kh\u00e1c v\u1ec1 chuy\u1ec3n nh\u01b0\u1ee3ng M.U tr\u00ean trang bongda24h.vn:<br>\r\n<br>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelatepannel\">\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate\"><span href=\"/bong-da-anh/zizou-da-san-sang-thay-jose-mourinho-o-mu-172-194539.html\">Zizou \u0111\u00e3 s\u1eb5n s\u00e0ng thay Jose Mourinho \u1edf M.U</span></div>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate\"><span href=\"/bong-da-anh/paul-pogba-len-tieng-ve-tuong-lai-cua-minh-172-194297.html\">T\u1ea1i sao Pogba ch\u01b0a c\u00f4ng khai mu\u1ed1n r\u1eddi M.U?</span></div>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate\"><span href=\"/bong-da-anh/mu-chuyen-nhuong-that-bai-den-nguoi-nha-con-bo-mac-mourinho-172-194167.html\">M.U chuy\u1ec3n nh\u01b0\u1ee3ng th\u1ea5t b\u00e1t: \u0110\u1ebfn \u201cng\u01b0\u1eddi nh\u00e0\u201d c\u00f2n b\u1ecf m\u1eb7c Mourinho!</span></div>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate\"><span href=\"/bong-da-anh/paul-pogba-hanh-phuc-tai-mu-172-194152.html\">Ph\u1ea3i \u1edf l\u1ea1i M.U, Pogba c\u00f3 c\u00f2n h\u1ea1nh ph\u00fac?</span></div>\r\n</div>\r\n<br>\r\n<br>\r\nGia Vi (TTVN)<br>\r\n</strong></div></div><advbottom>","new_url":"","id":"2567","checkdouble":"194879"},{"date":"10:52 20/08","title":"Real Madrid n\u00e2ng gi\u00e1 h\u1ecfi mua sao kh\u1ee7ng PSG l\u00ean 63 tri\u1ec7u b\u1ea3ng","type":"B\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 Anh","img_url":"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/7/6/real-madrid-nang-gia-hoi-mua-cavani-len-63-trieu-bang.jpg","new_desc":"<link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><h2>Real Madrid quy\u1ebft t\u00e2m mua Edinson Cavani, theo Diario Gol \u0111\u1ed9i ch\u1ee7 s\u00e2n Bernabeu \u0111\u00e3 n\u00e2ng gi\u00e1 h\u1ecfi mua c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 ng\u01b0\u1eddi Uruguay l\u00ean 63 tri\u1ec7u b\u1ea3ng.\r\n</h2><h2 style=\"text-align: justify;\">PSG t\u1eeb ch\u1ed1i b\u00e1n Cavani cho Real</h2>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nReal Madrid \u0111\u00e3 kh\u00f4ng th\u1ec3 gi\u1eef Ronaldo \u1edf l\u1ea1i Bernabeu, ng\u00f4i sao ng\u01b0\u1eddi B\u1ed3 \u0110\u00e0o Nha \u0111\u00e3 quy\u1ebft \u0111\u1ecbnh \u0111\u1ea7u qu\u00e2n cho Juventus. Los Blancos \u0111\u00e3 t\u00edch c\u1ef1c \u0111\u01b0a v\u1ec1 nh\u00e2n t\u1ed1 thay th\u1ebf, song g\u1eb7p r\u1ea5t nhi\u1ec1u kh\u00f3 kh\u0103n.<br>\r\n\u00a0</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width: 100%;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"Chi 63 tri\u1ec7u b\u1ea3ng, Real Madrid quy\u1ebft t\u00e2m mua Edinson Cavani h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" title=\"Chi 63 tri\u1ec7u b\u1ea3ng, Real Madrid quy\u1ebft t\u00e2m mua Edinson Cavani h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/7/6/Chi-63-trieu-bang,-Real-Madrid-quyet-tam-mua-Edinson-Cavani-hinh-anh.PNG\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td>\r\n            <h3>PSG t\u1eeb ch\u1ed1i b\u00e1n Cavani cho Real Madrid</h3>\r\n            </td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<br>\r\nNeymar, Mbappe v\u00e0 Hazard l\u00e0 3 m\u1ee5c ti\u00eau h\u00e0ng \u0111\u1ea7u c\u1ee7a Real Madrid, song nh\u1eefng th\u01b0\u01a1ng v\u1ee5 n\u00e0y \u0111\u1ec1u kh\u00f4ng th\u1ec3 th\u00e0nh c\u00f4ng. N\u1ebfu nh\u01b0 PSG h\u00e9t gi\u00e1 si\u00eau kh\u1ee7ng cho Neymar v\u00e0 Mbappe th\u00ec Hazard l\u1ea1i cam k\u1ebft g\u1eafn b\u00f3 v\u1edbi Chelsea.</div>\r\n</div><mobileadv><link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nHLV Lopetegui r\u1ea5t mu\u1ed1n \u0111\u01b0a v\u1ec1 m\u1ed9t ti\u1ec1n \u0111\u1ea1o \u0111\u1eb3ng c\u1ea5p \u0111\u1ec3 c\u1ea1nh tranh v\u1edbi Karim Benzema, K\u1ec1n k\u1ec1n tr\u1eafng \u0111\u00e3 nh\u1eafm t\u1edbi Edinson Cavani c\u1ee7a PSG. \u0110\u1ed9i ch\u1ee7 s\u00e2n Bernabeu ch\u1ea5p nh\u1eadn chi 53 tri\u1ec7u b\u1ea3ng cho th\u01b0\u01a1ng v\u1ee5 n\u00e0y.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nTuy nhi\u00ean, PSG \u0111\u00e3 t\u1eeb ch\u1ed1i b\u00e1n ch\u00e2n s\u00fat 31 tu\u1ed5i cho \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng c\u1ee7a T\u00e2y Ban Nha. <span href=\"https://bongda24h.vn/bong-da-phap/hlv-psg-len-tieng-ve-tuong-lai-edinson-cavani-197-192355.html\" target=\"_blank\">HLV Thomas Tuchel n\u00f3i v\u1ec1 t\u01b0\u01a1ng lai Cavani</span>, \u00f4ng th\u1ea7y ng\u01b0\u1eddi \u0110\u1ee9c kh\u1eb3ng \u0111\u1ecbnh \u01b0u ti\u00ean gi\u1eef c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 ng\u01b0\u1eddi Uruguay \u1edf l\u1ea1i, \u00f4ng s\u1ebd kh\u00f4ng \u0111\u1ec3 anh ra \u0111i \u1edf H\u00e8 2018.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">\u00a0</div>\r\n<h2>Real n\u00e2ng gi\u00e1 h\u1ecfi mua Cavani</h2>\r\n<h2>\u00a0</h2>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">M\u1eb7c d\u00f9 ph\u00eda PSG t\u1ecf ra r\u1ea5t c\u1ee9ng r\u1eafn, song Real Madrid v\u1eabn nu\u00f4i hy v\u1ecdng s\u1edf h\u1eefu c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 sinh n\u0103m 1987. Trong m\u1ed9t di\u1ec5n bi\u1ebfn m\u1edbi nh\u1ea5t, \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng c\u1ee7a TBN v\u1eeba c\u00f3 th\u00eam m\u1ed9t \u0111\u1ed9ng th\u00e1i \u0111\u1ec3 chi\u00eau m\u1ed9 ng\u00f4i sao 31 tu\u1ed5i.<br>\r\n\u00a0</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width: 100%;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"Real Madrid n\u00e2ng gi\u00e1 h\u1ecfi mua sao kh\u1ee7ng PSG l\u00ean 63 tri\u1ec7u b\u1ea3ng h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh 2\" title=\"Real Madrid n\u00e2ng gi\u00e1 h\u1ecfi mua sao kh\u1ee7ng PSG l\u00ean 63 tri\u1ec7u b\u1ea3ng h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh 2\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/1/18/Real-Madrid-nang-gia-hoi-mua-sao-khung-PSG-len-63-trieu-bang-hinh-anh-2.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td>\r\n            <h3>Real n\u00e2ng gi\u00e1 h\u1ecfi mua Edinson Cavani l\u00ean 63 tri\u1ec7u b\u1ea3ng</h3>\r\n            </td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<br>\r\nReal Madrid quy\u1ebft t\u00e2m mua Edinson Cavani, theo Diario Gol \u0111\u1ed9i ch\u1ee7 s\u00e2n Bernabeu \u0111\u00e3 n\u00e2ng gi\u00e1 h\u1ecfi mua c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 ng\u01b0\u1eddi Uruguay l\u00ean 63 tri\u1ec7u b\u1ea3ng.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nHLV Lopetegui tin r\u1eb1ng Cavani s\u1ebd t\u1ea1o ra s\u1ef1 c\u1ea1nh tranh v\u1edbi Benzema, \u00f4ng th\u1ea7y ng\u01b0\u1eddi T\u00e2y Ban Nha c\u0169ng t\u1ecf ra \u1ea5n t\u01b0\u1ee3ng v\u1edbi kh\u1ea3 n\u0103ng s\u0103n b\u00e0n c\u1ee7a c\u1ef1u sao Napoli.\u00a0</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\n63 tri\u1ec7u b\u1ea3ng cho m\u1ed9t ti\u1ec1n \u0111\u1ea1o 31 tu\u1ed5i l\u00e0 s\u1ed1 ti\u1ec1n kh\u00f4ng h\u1ec1 nh\u1ecf, nh\u01b0ng PSG s\u1ebd ch\u1ec9 ch\u1ea5p nh\u1eadn b\u00e1n Cavani cho Real n\u1ebfu t\u00ecm \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c ng\u01b0\u1eddi thay th\u1ebf.\u00a0</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\n\u1ede th\u1eddi \u0111i\u1ec3m hi\u1ec7n t\u1ea1i \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng n\u01b0\u1edbc Ph\u00e1p kh\u00f4ng d\u1ec5 \u0111\u1ec3 t\u00ecm \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c ng\u01b0\u1eddi thay Cavani, nh\u1eefng m\u1ee5c ti\u00eau h\u00e0ng \u0111\u1ea7u c\u1ee7a h\u1ecd nh\u01b0 Morata hay Lewandowski \u0111\u1ec1u \u0111ang r\u1ea5t kh\u00f3 kh\u0103n. N\u1ebfu PSG kh\u00f4ng mua \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c m\u1ed9t ch\u00e2n s\u00fat t\u1ed1t, nhi\u1ec1u kh\u1ea3 n\u0103ng h\u1ecd s\u1ebd t\u1eeb ch\u1ed1i b\u00e1n Cavani cho Los Blancos.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nL\u00ea H\u01b0\u1eddng (TTVN)</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">\u00a0</div></div><advbottom>","new_url":"","id":"2566","checkdouble":"194880"},{"date":"10:26 20/08","title":"Morata: \"T\u00f4i ch\u01b0a t\u1eebng ngh\u0129 \u0111\u1ebfn chuy\u1ec7n r\u1eddi Chelsea\"","type":"B\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 Anh","img_url":"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/8/20/morata-toi-chua-tung-nghi-den-chuyen-roi-chelsea.jpg","new_desc":"<link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><h2>Ti\u1ec1n \u0111\u1ea1o Alvaro Morata kh\u1eb3ng \u0111\u1ecbnh anh ch\u01b0a t\u1eebng ngh\u0129 \u0111\u1ebfn vi\u1ec7c r\u1eddi Chelsea v\u00e0 mong mu\u1ed1n tr\u1edf th\u00e0nh ch\u00e2n s\u00fat ch\u1ee7 l\u1ef1c c\u1ee7a \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng th\u00e0nh London.</h2><h2>Morata ph\u1ee7 nh\u1eadn tin \u0111\u1ed3n mu\u1ed1n r\u1eddi Chelsea</h2>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">Morata m\u1edbi ghi \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c 1 b\u00e0n th\u1eafng \u1edf Premier League trong n\u0103m 2018. \u0110i\u1ec1u \u0111\u00f3 khi\u1ebfn cho nh\u1eefng tin \u0111\u1ed3n v\u1ec1 t\u01b0\u01a1ng lai c\u1ee7a anh b\u1ecb truy\u1ec1n th\u00f4ng d\u1ea5y l\u00ean. R\u1ea5t nhi\u1ec1u c\u00e1i t\u00ean \u1edf Serie A c\u0169ng nh\u01b0 La Liga \u0111\u00e3 \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c li\u00ean h\u1ec7 v\u1edbi Morata trong th\u1eddi gian g\u1ea7n \u0111\u00e2y.<br>\r\n<br>\r\nNh\u01b0ng ng\u00f4i sao 25 tu\u1ed5i \u0111ang \u0111\u00f3ng m\u1ed9t vai tr\u00f2 quan tr\u1ecdng trong \u0111\u1ed9i h\u00ecnh c\u1ee7a t\u00e2n HLV Sarri. C\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 ng\u01b0\u1eddi T\u00e2y Ban Nha c\u0169ng m\u1edbi \u0111\u00f3ng g\u00f3p 1 b\u00e0n trong chi\u1ebfn th\u1eafng c\u1ee7a The Blues tr\u01b0\u1edbc k\u00ecnh \u0111\u1ecbch Arsenal h\u00f4m th\u1ee9 B\u1ea3y.<br>\r\n<br>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width:100%; text-align: center;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"Morata ph\u00e1t bi\u1ec3u v\u1ec1 tin \u0111\u1ed3n r\u1eddi Chelsea h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" title=\"Morata ph\u00e1t bi\u1ec3u v\u1ec1 tin \u0111\u1ed3n r\u1eddi Chelsea h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/8/20/morata-toi-chua-tung-nghi-den-chuyen-roi-chelsea.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td style=\"text-align: center\">\r\n            <h3>Morata ph\u1ee7 nh\u1eadn tin \u0111\u1ed3n mu\u1ed1n r\u1eddi Chelsea</h3>\r\n            </td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<br>\r\nV\u00e0 trong b\u00e0i ph\u00e1t bi\u1ec3u m\u1edbi \u0111\u00e2y, Morata quy\u1ebft t\u00e2m x\u00f3a h\u1ebft nh\u1eefng v\u1ea5n \u0111\u1ec1 c\u1ee7a m\u00ecnh \u1edf Chelsea d\u01b0\u1edbi s\u1ef1 d\u1eabn d\u1eaft c\u1ee7a HLV Sarri.<br>\r\n<br>\r\n<em>\u201cT\u00f4i ch\u01b0a bao gi\u1edd ngh\u0129 t\u1edbi vi\u1ec7c ra \u0111i. V\u1edbi t\u00f4i, quy\u1ebft \u0111\u1ecbnh \u1edf l\u1ea1i l\u00e0 r\u1ea5t d\u1ec5 d\u00e0ng. T\u00f4i c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 tr\u1edf l\u1ea1i T\u00e2y Ban Nha ho\u1eb7c Italia. \u1ede \u0111\u00f3, m\u1ecdi ng\u01b0\u1eddi tin t\u01b0\u1edfng </em><em>v\u00e0o t\u00f4i. Nh\u01b0ng t\u00f4i mu\u1ed1n thay \u0111\u1ed5i m\u1ecdi th\u1ee9 \u1edf \u0111\u00e2y. T\u00f4i mu\u1ed1n l\u00e0m \u0111i\u1ec1u \u0111\u00f3, kh\u00f4ng ph\u1ea3i v\u00ec nh\u1eefng k\u1ebb th\u00f9 gh\u00e9t t\u00f4i m\u00e0 t\u00f4i mu\u1ed1n c\u1ed1 g\u1eafng cho ch\u00ednh t\u00f4i v\u00e0 cho Chelsea.<br>\r\n<br>\r\n\u201cT\u00f4i \u0111ang t\u00ednh chuy\u1ec7n mua nh\u00e0 v\u00e0 t\u00f4i mong mu\u1ed1n c\u00f3 nh\u1eefng \u0111\u1ee9a b\u00e9 l\u1edbn l\u00ean v\u00e0 \u0111i h\u1ecdc \u1edf \u0111\u00e2y. T\u00f4i r\u1ea5t h\u1ea1nh ph\u00fac v\u00e0 \u0111\u00e2y m\u1edbi ch\u1ec9 l\u00e0 kh\u1edfi \u0111\u1ea7u c\u1ee7a m\u00f9a gi\u1ea3i m\u1edbi. T\u1ea1i sao t\u00f4i l\u1ea1i kh\u00f4ng h\u1ea1nh ph\u00fac ch\u1ee9. T\u00f4i mu\u1ed1n thay \u0111\u1ed5i suy ngh\u0129 c\u1ee7a nh\u1eefng ng\u01b0\u1eddi cho r\u1eb1ng t\u00f4i kh\u00f4ng h\u1ea1nh ph\u00fac.<br>\r\n<br>\r\n\u201c\u0110\u00f3 l\u00e0 l\u00fd do t\u00f4i \u1edf l\u1ea1i \u0111\u00e2y. C\u00f2n n\u1ebfu Chelsea n\u00f3i r\u1eb1ng t\u00f4i kh\u00f4ng ph\u00f9 h\u1ee3p v\u1edbi k\u1ebf ho\u1ea1ch c\u1ee7a \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng th\u00ec t\u00f4i s\u1ebd ra \u0111i.<br>\r\n<br>\r\n\u201c\u0110i\u1ec1u quan tr\u1ecdng nh\u1ea5t l\u00e0 c\u00e1ch ch\u00fang t\u00f4i thi \u0111\u1ea5u. M\u00f9a tr\u01b0\u1edbc, t\u00f4i \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c giao nhi\u1ec7m v\u1ee5 \u0111\u00f3n b\u00f3ng t\u1eeb nh\u1eefng \u0111\u01b0\u1eddng chuy\u1ec1n v\u01b0\u1ee3t tuy\u1ebfn v\u00e0 l\u00e0m t\u01b0\u1eddng. Nh\u01b0ng ch\u01a1i b\u00f3ng b\u1ed5ng kh\u00f4ng ph\u1ea3i s\u1edf tr\u01b0\u1eddng c\u1ee7a t\u00f4i. Gi\u1edd thi t\u00f4i c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 t\u1ea5n c\u00f4ng v\u00e0o c\u00e1c kho\u1ea3ng tr\u1ed1ng. T\u00f4i c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 \u0111\u00e1 m\u1ed9t ch\u1ea1m v\u00e0 \u0111\u00e9n nh\u1eefng v\u1ecb tr\u00ed t\u1ed1t nh\u1ea5t \u0111\u1ec3 \u0111\u00f3n c\u00e1c qu\u1ea3 t\u1ea1t. M\u1ecdi th\u1ee9 c\u00f3 v\u1ebb \u0111\u00e3 t\u1ed1t h\u01a1n nhi\u1ec1u v\u1edbi t\u00f4i\u201d.</em><br>\r\n<br>\r\n<strong>Xem th\u00eam nh\u1eefng tin t\u1ee9c kh\u00e1c v\u1ec1 Chelsea:</strong><br>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelatepannel\">\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate\"><span href=\"/bong-da-anh/khong-mot-cau-thu-nao-cua-arsenal-du-suc-dung-trong-doi-hinh-chelsea-172-194868.html\">Kh\u00f4ng m\u1ed9t c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 n\u00e0o c\u1ee7a Arsenal \u0111\u1ee7 s\u1ee9c \u0111\u1ee9ng trong \u0111\u1ed9i h\u00ecnh Chelsea</span></div>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate\"><span href=\"/bong-da-anh/tan-binh-kovacic-noi-gi-sau-man-ra-mat-chelsea-172-194861.html\">T\u00e2n binh Kovacic n\u00f3i g\u00ec sau m\u00e0n ra m\u1eaft Chelsea?</span></div>\r\n</div>\r\n<br>\r\n<br>\r\n<strong>Xu\u00e2n Phong (TTVN)</strong></div></div><advbottom>","new_url":"","id":"2565","checkdouble":"194881"},{"date":"10:49 20/08","title":"Huy\u1ec1n tho\u1ea1i M.U ch\u1ec9 tr\u00edch l\u00e3nh \u0111\u1ea1o b\u1ecf m\u1eb7c Mourinho","type":"B\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 Anh","img_url":"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/8/20/gary-neville-phat-bieu-ve-mu.jpg","new_desc":"<link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><h2>Gary Neville ph\u00e1t bi\u1ec3u v\u1ec1 M.U. C\u1ef1u danh th\u1ee7 n\u00e0y tin r\u1eb1ng l\u00e3nh \u0111\u1ea1o Qu\u1ef7 \u0111\u1ecf \u0111\u00e3 thi\u1ebfu \u0111i s\u1ef1 h\u1ed7 tr\u1ee3 v\u1edbi HLV Jose Mourinho trong c\u00f4ng t\u00e1c chuy\u1ec3n nh\u01b0\u1ee3ng.</h2><div style=\"text-align: justify;\">\u00a0</div>\r\n<h2>M.U tr\u1ea3 gi\u00e1 v\u00ec chuy\u1ec3n nh\u01b0\u1ee3ng th\u1ea5t b\u1ea1i</h2>\r\n</div><mobileadv><link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nM\u00f9a h\u00e8 n\u00e0y, Man United ch\u1ec9 mang v\u1ec1 3 t\u00e2n binh bao g\u1ed3m ti\u1ec1n v\u1ec7 Fred, h\u1eadu v\u1ec7 c\u00e1nh Diogo Dalot v\u00e0 th\u1ee7 m\u00f4n Lee Grant. Tuy nhi\u00ean, ch\u1ec9 1 trong s\u1ed1 n\u00e0y l\u00e0 Fred v\u1eeba \u00fd HLV Jose Mourinho. Nh\u1eefng Dalot non kinh nghi\u1ec7m hay Grant l\u1edbn tu\u1ed5i \u0111\u1ec1u kh\u00f4ng ph\u1ea3i nh\u1eefng gi\u1ea3i ph\u00e1p t\u1ee9c th\u00ec.<br>\r\n<br>\r\n\u0110\u00e3 xu\u1ea5t hi\u1ec7n nh\u1eefng tin \u0111\u1ed3n v\u1ec1 vi\u1ec7c M.U li\u00ean h\u1ec7 v\u1edbi Toby Alderweireld c\u1ee7a Tottenham v\u00e0 Harry Maguire c\u1ee7a Leicester City. Tuy nhi\u00ean, \u0111\u1ebfn cu\u1ed1i phi\u00ean ch\u1ee3 h\u00e8 2018 d\u00e0nh cho c\u00e1c CLB Premier League, kh\u00f4ng c\u00f3 th\u00eam b\u1ea5t c\u1ee9 ai c\u1eadp b\u1ebfn Old Trafford.<br>\r\n<br>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width:100%; text-align: center;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"Gary Neville ph\u00e1t bi\u1ec3u v\u1ec1 MU v\u00e0 Mourinho h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" title=\"Gary Neville ph\u00e1t bi\u1ec3u v\u1ec1 MU v\u00e0 Mourinho h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/8/20/Gary-Neville-phat-bieu-ve-MU-va-Mourinho-hinh-anh.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td style=\"text-align: center\">M.U \u0111ang c\u00f3 nh\u1eefng k\u1ebft qu\u1ea3 kh\u00f4ng t\u1ed1t</td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<br>\r\nH\u1ec7 qu\u1ea3 l\u00e0 M.U c\u00f3 nh\u1eefng m\u00e0n tr\u00ecnh di\u1ec5n k\u00e9m thuy\u1ebft ph\u1ee5c tr\u00ean s\u00e2n c\u1ecf. T\u1ea1i Premier League, sau chi\u1ebfn th\u1eafng 2-1 ch\u1eadt v\u1eadt tr\u01b0\u1edbc Leicester, h\u1ecd th\u1ea5t th\u1ee7 2-3 tr\u00ean s\u00e2n Brighton \u0111\u1ec3 l\u1ea1i nhi\u1ec1u lo l\u1eafng cho ng\u01b0\u1eddi h\u00e2m m\u1ed9.<br>\r\n\u00a0</div>\r\n<h2>Neville ch\u1ec9 tr\u00edch l\u00e3nh \u0111\u1ea1o M.U</h2>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nC\u1ef1u \u0111\u1ed9i tr\u01b0\u1edfng Gary Neville ph\u00e1t bi\u1ec3u v\u1ec1 M.U. Anh tin r\u1eb1ng Gi\u00e1m \u0111\u1ed1c \u0111i\u1ec1u h\u00e0nh Ed Woodward c\u00f9ng l\u00e3nh \u0111\u1ea1o Qu\u1ef7 \u0111\u1ecf c\u1ea7n h\u1ed7 tr\u1ee3 Mourinho trong mua s\u1eafm n\u1ebfu mu\u1ed1n b\u00f9 \u0111\u1eafp cho nh\u1eefng sai l\u1ea7m c\u1ee7a qu\u00e1 kh\u1ee9 sau khi Alex Ferguson ngh\u1ec9 h\u01b0u v\u00e0o n\u0103m 2013.<br>\r\n<br>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width:100%; text-align: center;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"HLV Mourinho\" title=\"HLV Mourinho\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/8/20/gary-neville-phat-bieu-ve-mu.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td style=\"text-align: center\">\r\n            <h3>Gary Neville ph\u00e1t bi\u1ec3u v\u1ec1 M.U v\u00e0 Mourinho</h3>\r\n            </td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<br>\r\n\u201cMourinho \u0111ang \u1edf m\u00f9a gi\u1ea3i th\u1ee9 3 v\u00e0 t\u00f4i ngh\u0129 \u00f4ng \u1ea5y s\u1ebd c\u1ea3m th\u1ea5y v\u00f4 c\u00f9ng th\u1ea5t v\u1ecdng khi kh\u00f4ng nh\u1eadn \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c h\u1ed7 tr\u1ee3 tr\u00ean th\u1ecb tr\u01b0\u1eddng chuy\u1ec3n nh\u01b0\u1ee3ng\u201d, Neville n\u00f3i tr\u00ean Sky Sports. \u201cB\u1ea1n kh\u00f4ng th\u1ec3 \u0111\u1ec3 m\u1ed9t ng\u00f4i nh\u00e0 v\u1edbi 3/4 l\u00e0 \u0111ang x\u00e2y d\u1ef1ng. B\u1ea1n ph\u1ea3i ho\u00e0n th\u00e0nh n\u00f3 v\u00e0 ho\u00e0n th\u00e0nh vi\u1ec7c x\u00e2y d\u1ef1ng. Sau \u0111\u00f3, b\u1ea1n m\u1edbi c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 ngh\u0129 v\u1ec1 vi\u1ec7c b\u00e1n ho\u1eb7c cho thu\u00ea n\u00f3.\u201d<br>\r\n<br>\r\n\u201cKh\u00f4ng ai nh\u1eadn ng\u00f4i nh\u00e0 \u0111\u00f3 n\u1ebfu n\u00f3 c\u00f2n dang d\u1edf. M.U \u0111\u00e3 g\u1eb7p v\u1ea5n \u0111\u1ec1 tr\u00ean th\u1ecb tr\u01b0\u1eddng chuy\u1ec3n nh\u01b0\u1ee3ng k\u1ec3 t\u1eeb khi Sir Alex Ferguson ngh\u1ec9 h\u01b0u. Nh\u1eefng David Moyes v\u00e0 sau \u0111\u00f3 l\u00e0 Louis van Gaal \u0111\u00e3 chi kh\u00f4ng d\u01b0\u1edbi 700 tri\u1ec7u b\u1ea3ng nh\u01b0ng kh\u00f4ng mang l\u1ea1i gi\u00e1 tr\u1ecb.\u201d<br>\r\n<br>\r\n\u201cMourinho c\u1ea7n \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c \u0111\u1ea7u t\u01b0 th\u00eam. R\u00f5 r\u00e0ng l\u00e0 CLB n\u00ean h\u1ed7 tr\u1ee3 \u00f4ng \u1ea5y. B\u1ea1n kh\u00f4ng th\u1ec3 h\u1ee7y b\u1ecf m\u1ed9t d\u1ef1 \u00e1n khi c\u00f2n \u0111ang trong qu\u00e1 tr\u00ecnh x\u00e2y d\u1ef1ng. Kh\u00f4ng d\u1ec5 d\u00e0ng \u0111\u1ec3 c\u1ea1nh tranh c\u00e1c danh hi\u1ec7u trong t\u00ecnh h\u00ecnh hi\u1ec7n nay.\u201d<br>\r\n<strong><br>\r\nXem th\u00eam m\u1ed9t s\u1ed1 b\u00e0i vi\u1ebft kh\u00e1c v\u1ec1 chuy\u1ec3n nh\u01b0\u1ee3ng M.U tr\u00ean trang bongda24h.vn:<br>\r\n<br>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelatepannel\">\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate\"><span href=\"/bong-da-anh/zizou-da-san-sang-thay-jose-mourinho-o-mu-172-194539.html\">Zizou \u0111\u00e3 s\u1eb5n s\u00e0ng thay Jose Mourinho \u1edf M.U</span></div>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate\"><span href=\"/bong-da-anh/paul-pogba-len-tieng-ve-tuong-lai-cua-minh-172-194297.html\">T\u1ea1i sao Pogba ch\u01b0a c\u00f4ng khai mu\u1ed1n r\u1eddi M.U?</span></div>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate\"><span href=\"/bong-da-anh/mu-chuyen-nhuong-that-bai-den-nguoi-nha-con-bo-mac-mourinho-172-194167.html\">M.U chuy\u1ec3n nh\u01b0\u1ee3ng th\u1ea5t b\u00e1t: \u0110\u1ebfn \u201cng\u01b0\u1eddi nh\u00e0\u201d c\u00f2n b\u1ecf m\u1eb7c Mourinho!</span></div>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate\"><span href=\"/bong-da-anh/paul-pogba-hanh-phuc-tai-mu-172-194152.html\">Ph\u1ea3i \u1edf l\u1ea1i M.U, Pogba c\u00f3 c\u00f2n h\u1ea1nh ph\u00fac?</span></div>\r\n</div>\r\n<br>\r\n<br>\r\nGia Vi (TTVN)<br>\r\n</strong></div></div><advbottom>","new_url":"","id":"2564","checkdouble":"194883"},{"date":"11:35 20/08","title":"Man City chi 60 tri\u1ec7u b\u1ea3ng mua Ruben Neves v\u00e0o th\u00e1ng 1","type":"B\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 Anh","img_url":"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/8/20/man-city-chi-60-trieu-bang-mua-ruben-neves-vao-thang-1.PNG","new_desc":"<link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><h2>Man City mu\u1ed1n mua Ruben Neves c\u1ee7a Wolves, \u0111\u1ed9i ch\u1ee7 s\u00e2n Etihad ch\u1ea5p nh\u1eadn chi t\u1edbi 60 tri\u1ec7u b\u1ea3ng cho th\u01b0\u01a1ng v\u1ee5 n\u00e0y.\r\n</h2><h2 style=\"text-align: justify;\">Pep kh\u00e1t khao m\u1ed9t ti\u1ec1n v\u1ec7 trung t\u00e2m \u0111\u1eb3ng c\u1ea5p</h2>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\n\u1ede k\u1ef3 chuy\u1ec3n nh\u01b0\u1ee3ng H\u00e8 2018, HLV Pep Guardiola \u0111\u00e3 quy\u1ebft t\u00e2m \u0111\u01b0a v\u1ec1 m\u1ed9t ti\u1ec1n v\u1ec7 trung t\u00e2m \u0111\u1eb3ng c\u1ea5p. Jorginho l\u00e0 m\u1ee5c ti\u00eau h\u00e0ng \u0111\u1ea7u c\u1ee7a Man xanh, song c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 n\u00e0y \u0111\u00e3 t\u1eeb ch\u1ed1i Etihad \u0111\u1ec3 \u0111o\u00e0n t\u1ee5 v\u1edbi th\u1ea7y c\u0169 Sarri \u1edf Chelsea.<br>\r\n\u00a0</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width: 100%;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"Man City mu\u1ed1n mua Ruben Neves v\u1edbi gi\u00e1 60 tri\u1ec7u b\u1ea3ng h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" title=\"Man City mu\u1ed1n mua Ruben Neves v\u1edbi gi\u00e1 60 tri\u1ec7u b\u1ea3ng h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/8/20/Man-City-muon-mua-Ruben-Neves-voi-gia-60-trieu-bang-hinh-anh.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td>\r\n            <h3>Pep Guardiola mu\u1ed1n mua th\u00eam ti\u1ec1n v\u1ec7 trung t\u00e2m</h3>\r\n            </td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<br>\r\nSau khi th\u1ea5t b\u1ea1i v\u1ee5 Jorginho, Man City \u0111\u00e3 chuy\u1ec3n h\u01b0\u1edbng sang Aaron Ramsey c\u1ee7a Arsenal v\u00e0 Sergej Milinkovic-Savic c\u1ee7a Lazio. Tuy nhi\u00ean, Man City \u0111\u00e3 th\u1ea5t b\u1ea1i trong c\u1ea3 hai th\u01b0\u01a1ng v\u1ee5 n\u00e0y, n\u1ebfu nh\u01b0 Arsenal quy\u1ebft gi\u1eef Ramsey th\u00ec Lazio h\u00e9t gi\u00e1 110 tri\u1ec7u euro cho Milinkovic-Savic.</div>\r\n</div><mobileadv><link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nKh\u00f4ng mua \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c ti\u1ec1n v\u1ec7 trung t\u00e2m \u0111\u1eb3ng c\u1ea5p \u1edf H\u00e8 2018, Pep \u0111\u00e3 l\u00ean k\u1ebf ho\u1ea1ch \u0111\u01b0a v\u1ec1 m\u1ed9t ti\u1ec1n v\u1ec7 \u0111\u1eb3ng c\u1ea5p v\u00e0o th\u00e1ng 1 t\u1edbi \u0111\u00e2y. Vi\u1ec7c <span href=\"https://bongda24h.vn/bong-da-anh/man-city-nhan-tin-cuc-soc-ve-de-bruyne-172-194571.html\" target=\"_blank\">Kevin de Bruyne d\u00ednh ch\u1ea5n th\u01b0\u01a1ng</span> 3 th\u00e1ng c\u00f2n David Silva tuy\u00ean b\u1ed1 kh\u00f4ng ra s\u00e2n th\u01b0\u1eddng xuy\u00ean bu\u1ed9c Pep ph\u1ea3i mua th\u00eam ti\u1ec1n v\u1ec7.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nNh\u1eefng m\u1ee5c ti\u00eau m\u00e0 \u00f4ng th\u1ea7y ng\u01b0\u1eddi T\u00e2y Ban Nha nh\u1eafm t\u1edbi c\u0169ng \u0111\u00e3 \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c \u0111\u01b0a v\u00e0o t\u1ea7m ng\u1eafm, Ruben Neves l\u00e0 m\u1ed9t trong nh\u1eefng c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c Pep quan t\u00e2m.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">\u00a0</div>\r\n<h2>Man City t\u00ednh chi 60 tri\u1ec7u b\u1ea3ng mua Ruben Neves</h2>\r\n<h2>\u00a0</h2>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">Man City mu\u1ed1n mua Ruben Neves c\u1ee7a Wolves, \u0111\u1ed9i ch\u1ee7 s\u00e2n Etihad ch\u1ea5p nh\u1eadn chi t\u1edbi 60 tri\u1ec7u b\u1ea3ng cho th\u01b0\u01a1ng v\u1ee5 n\u00e0y.<br>\r\n\u00a0</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width: 100%;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"Man City muon mua Ruben Neves\" title=\"Man City mu\u1ed1n mua Ruben Neves\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/8/20/man-city-chi-60-trieu-bang-mua-ruben-neves-vao-thang-1.PNG\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td>\r\n            <h3>Man City mu\u1ed1n mua Ruben Neves</h3>\r\n            </td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<br>\r\nM\u00f9a gi\u1ea3i v\u1eeba qua Ruben Neves l\u00e0 tr\u1ee5 c\u1ed9t kh\u00f4ng th\u1ec3 thay th\u1ebf trong \u0111\u1ed9i h\u00ecnh c\u1ee7a Wolves, c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 21 tu\u1ed5i s\u1edf tr\u01b0\u1eddng \u0111\u00e1 ti\u1ec1n v\u1ec7 trung t\u00e2m nh\u01b0ng khi c\u1ea7n anh c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 \u0111\u00e1 c\u00e1nh ho\u1eb7c h\u1ed9 c\u00f4ng.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nNg\u00f4i sao ng\u01b0\u1eddi B\u1ed3 \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c \u0111\u00e1nh gi\u00e1 l\u00e0 m\u1eabu ti\u1ec1n v\u1ec7 trung t\u00e2m to\u00e0n n\u0103ng, anh v\u1eeba c\u00f3 kh\u1ea3 n\u0103ng thu h\u1ed3i b\u00f3ng, ph\u00e1t \u0111\u1ed9ng t\u1ea5n c\u00f4ng, ki\u1ebfn t\u1ea1o v\u00e0 ghi b\u00e0n.\u00a0M\u00e0n tr\u00ecnh di\u1ec5n \u1ea5n t\u01b0\u1ee3ng c\u1ee7a c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 sinh n\u0103m 1997 khi\u1ebfn Pep \u1ea5n t\u01b0\u1ee3ng, \u00f4ng mu\u1ed1n Man xanh chi m\u1ed9t s\u1ed1 ti\u1ec1n l\u1edbn mua c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 21 tu\u1ed5i.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nS\u1ed1 ti\u1ec1n 60 tri\u1ec7u b\u1ea3ng m\u00e0 Man City chi ra l\u00e0 c\u1ef1c l\u1edbn, b\u1edfi v\u1eady kh\u1ea3 n\u0103ng h\u1ecd chi\u00eau m\u1ed9 th\u00e0nh c\u00f4ng Ruben Neves l\u00e0 ho\u00e0n to\u00e0n c\u00f3 th\u1ec3. Ng\u00f4i sao 21 tu\u1ed5i \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c v\u00ed nh\u01b0 \u201cAndrea Pirlo m\u1edbi\u201d, b\u1edfi v\u1eady anh s\u1ebd l\u00e0 s\u1ef1 b\u1ed5 sung tuy\u1ec7t v\u1eddi cho \u0111\u1ed9i ch\u1ee7 s\u00e2n Etihad.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nV\u01b0\u01a1ng Ng\u00e2n (TTVN)</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">\u00a0</div></div><advbottom>","new_url":"","id":"2563","checkdouble":"194884"},{"date":"10:46 20/08","title":"Nh\u1eadn \u0111\u1ecbnh U23 Indonesia vs U23 Hong Kong 19h00 ng\u00e0y 20/8 (ASIAD 2018)","type":"B\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 Anh","img_url":"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/8/20/nhan-dinh-u23-indonesia-vs-u23-hong-kong-19h00-ngay-208-asiad-2018.JPG","new_desc":"<link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><h2>U23 Indonesia vs U23 Hong Kong l\u00fac 19h00 ng\u00e0y 20/8 (V\u00f2ng b\u1ea3ng m\u00f4n b\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 nam Asian 2018): Nh\u1eadn \u0111\u1ecbnh b\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1, \u00fd ki\u1ebfn chuy\u00ean gia, d\u1ef1 \u0111o\u00e1n k\u1ebft qu\u1ea3, ph\u00e2n t\u00edch chuy\u00ean m\u00f4n, c\u00e1c th\u00f4ng tin, th\u1ed1ng k\u00ea b\u00ean l\u1ec1 tr\u01b0\u1edbc tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u.</h2><div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width:100%; text-align: center;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"Nh\u1eadn \u0111\u1ecbnh U23 Indonesia vs U23 Hong Kong 19h00 ng\u00e0y 208 ASIAD h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" title=\"Nh\u1eadn \u0111\u1ecbnh U23 Indonesia vs U23 Hong Kong 19h00 ng\u00e0y 208 ASIAD h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/8/20/u23hongkong.JPG\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td style=\"text-align: center\">U23 Indonesia vs U23 Hong Kong</td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<br>\r\n<h2 style=\"color: rgb(0, 0, 0); font-family: Arial, Verdana, sans-serif; font-style: normal; font-variant-ligatures: normal; font-variant-caps: normal; letter-spacing: normal; text-indent: 0px; text-transform: none; white-space: normal; word-spacing: 0px; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); text-decoration-style: initial; text-decoration-color: initial;\"><span href=\"https://bongda24h.vn/nhan-dinh-bong-da-c344-p1.html\" target=\"_blank\">Nh\u1eadn \u0111\u1ecbnh b\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1</span><span><span><span><span><span><span><span><span><span><span><span><span><span><span><span><span><span><span><span><span><span><span><span><span><span><span><span><span><span><span><span><span><span><span><span><span><span><span><span><span><span><span><span><span><span><span><span><span><span><span><span><span><span><span><span><span><span><span><span><span> </span></span></span></span>U23 Indonesia vs U23 Hong Kong: 3-1<br>\r\n</span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></h2>\r\n<div>V\u1edbi vi\u1ec7c ba b\u1ea3ng \u0111\u1ea5u (B,C,D) \u0111\u00e3 k\u1ebft th\u00fac v\u00e0o ng\u00e0y h\u00f4m qua th\u00ec b\u1ea3ng A g\u1ea7n nh\u01b0 ch\u1eafc ch\u1eafn s\u1ebd c\u00f3 3 \u0111\u1ed9i gi\u00e0nh quy\u1ec1n \u0111i ti\u1ebfp. Ch\u1ee7 nh\u00e0 ASIAD 2018, Indonesia tuy ch\u1ec9 \u0111\u1ee9ng th\u1ee9 3 b\u1ea3ng A song tr\u1eeb khi thua c\u1ef1c \u0111\u1eadm Hong Kong \u1edf l\u01b0\u1ee3t tr\u1eadn cu\u1ed1i n\u00e0y th\u00ec m\u1edbi b\u1ecb lo\u1ea1i. Tr\u00ean BXH 6 \u0111\u1ed9i x\u1ebfp h\u1ea1ng 3 c\u1ee7a c\u00e1c b\u1ea3ng (ch\u1ecdn l\u1ea5y 4 \u0111\u1ed9i c\u00f3 th\u00e0nh t\u00edch t\u1ed1t nh\u1ea5t v\u00e0o v\u00f2ng 1/8) th\u00ec U23 Indonesia \u0111ang c\u00f3 ch\u1ec9 s\u1ed1 t\u1ed1t nh\u1ea5t (3 \u0111i\u1ec3m, hi\u1ec7u s\u1ed1 +3. Do b\u1ea3ng A c\u00f3 5 \u0111\u1ed9i n\u00ean trong BXH c\u00e1c \u0111\u1ed9i \u0111\u1ee9ng th\u1ee9 3 \u1edf c\u00e1c b\u1ea3ng th\u00ec ri\u00eang Indonesia ph\u1ea3i b\u1ecf qua th\u00e0nh t\u00edch \u0111\u1ed1i \u0111\u00e2u v\u1edbi \u0111\u1ed9i x\u1ebfp cu\u1ed1i b\u1ea3ng A) trong khi U23 Pakistan tuy c\u00f3 3 \u0111i\u1ec3m nh\u01b0ng hi\u1ec7u s\u1ed1 t\u1eadn -6 c\u00f2n U23 Th\u00e1i Lan th\u1eadm ch\u00ed ch\u1ec9 c\u00f3 2 \u0111i\u1ec3m.\u00a0 <br>\r\n<br>\r\nNh\u01b0 v\u1eady, nh\u00ecn v\u00e0o c\u1ee5c di\u1ec7n tr\u00ean c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 th\u1ea5y chuy\u1ec7n\u00a0U23 Indonesia b\u1ecb lo\u1ea1i g\u1ea7n nh\u01b0 l\u00e0 chuy\u1ec7n kh\u00f4ng t\u01b0\u1edfng.\u00a0T\u1ea5t nhi\u00ean v\u1edbi t\u01b0 c\u00e1ch ch\u1ee7 nh\u00e0 Asiad 2018, U23 Indonesia \u0111\u1eddi n\u00e0o mu\u1ed1n v\u00e0o v\u00f2ng 1/8 theo c\u00e1ch x\u1ea5u h\u1ed5 nh\u01b0 th\u1ebf. Th\u1eadm ch\u00ed, h\u1ecd c\u00f2n quy\u1ebft chi\u1ebfn th\u1eafng \u0111\u1ec3 chi\u1ebfm l\u1ea5y ng\u00f4i \u0111\u1ea7u b\u1ea3ng hi\u1ec7n do U23 Palestine t\u1ea1m n\u1eafm gi\u1eef.<br>\r\n<br>\r\nC\u00e1c C\u0110V\u00a0Indonesia lu\u00f4n r\u1ea5t cu\u1ed3ng nhi\u1ec7t v\u00e0 s\u1eb5n s\u00e0ng c\u1ed5 v\u0169 \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng c\u00f3 \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c chi\u1ebfn th\u1eafng tr\u01b0\u1edbc U23 Hong\u00a0Kong, \u0111\u1ed9i \u0111\u00e3 ch\u00ednh th\u1ee9c c\u00f3 m\u1eb7t \u1edf v\u00f2ng 1/8 ch\u1ec9 l\u00e0 d\u01b0\u1edbi t\u01b0 c\u00e1ch x\u1ebfp th\u1ee9 m\u1ea5y b\u1ea3ng A m\u00e0 th\u00f4i. Do v\u1eady, \u00edt nhi\u1ec1u \u0111\u1ed9ng l\u1ef1c c\u1ee7a h\u1ecd kh\u00f4ng cao b\u1eb1ng \u0111\u1ed9i ch\u1ee7 nh\u00e0 b\u1edfi x\u00e9t cho c\u00f9ng v\u1edbi tr\u00ecnh \u0111\u1ed9 c\u1ee7a m\u00ecnh U23 Hong\u00a0Kong g\u1eb7p \u0111\u1ed9i n\u00e0o \u1edf v\u00f2ng 1/8 c\u0169ng nh\u01b0 nhau n\u00ean h\u1ecd kh\u00f4ng nh\u1ea5t thi\u1ebft ph\u1ea3i so \u0111o t\u00ednh to\u00e1n.<br>\r\n<br>\r\n\u0110\u1ed9i h\u00ecnh d\u1ef1 ki\u1ebfn c\u1ee7a 2 \u0111\u1ed9i<br>\r\nU23 Indonesia (4-3-3): Andritany, Putu Gede Juni, Zulfiandi, Evan Dimas, M.Rezaldi, Goncalves da, Stefano janjte, Febri, Ricky Fajrin, Hansamu Yama, Saddil.<br>\r\nU23 Hong Kong (4-3-3): Ho Chun Yuen; Recio Comi, Wang Kit Tsui, Hok Ming Lau, Lilley Nunez; Remo Dujardin, Chun Lok Tan, Lam Ka Wai; Ching Lung Cheng, Wai Keung Chung, Siu Wai Chiu.\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width:100%; text-align: center;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"Xep hang tai bang A\" title=\"X\u1ebfp h\u1ea1ng t\u1ea1i b\u1ea3ng A\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/8/20/bang-A.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td style=\"text-align: center\">X\u1ebfp h\u1ea1ng t\u1ea1i b\u1ea3ng A</td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n</div>\r\n<br>\r\n<br></div><advbottom>","new_url":"","id":"2562","checkdouble":"194885"},{"date":"10:47 20/08","title":"4 c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 ch\u01a1i t\u1ec7 nh\u1ea5t c\u1ee7a MU tr\u01b0\u1edbc Brighton","type":"B\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 Anh","img_url":"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/8/20/4-cau-thu-choi-te-nhat-cua-mu-truoc-brighton.jpg","new_desc":"<link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><h2>Brighton \u0111\u00e3 g\u00e2y ch\u1ea5n \u0111\u1ed9ng t\u1ea1i s\u00e2n Amex khi h\u1ea1 g\u1ee5c Man United c\u1ee7a Mourinho v\u00e0 ghi \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c t\u1edbi 3 b\u00e0n th\u1eafng. C\u00f9ng nh\u00ecn qua 4 c\u00e1i t\u00ean ch\u01a1i t\u1ec7 nh\u1ea5t c\u1ee7a Qu\u1ef7 \u0111\u1ecf \u1edf tr\u1eadn thua b\u1ea1c nh\u01b0\u1ee3c v\u1eeba qua.</h2><h2>B\u1ed9 \u0111\u00f4i trung v\u1ec7 Bailly &ndash; Lindelof\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width:100%; text-align: center;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"4 Qu\u1ef7 \u0111\u1ecf ch\u01a1i t\u1ec7 nh\u1ea5t \u1edf tr\u1eadn Brighton 3-2 MU h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" title=\"4 Qu\u1ef7 \u0111\u1ecf ch\u01a1i t\u1ec7 nh\u1ea5t \u1edf tr\u1eadn Brighton 3-2 MU h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/8/20/104406-1.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td style=\"text-align: center\">\r\n            <h3>C\u1eb7p \u0111\u00f4i trung v\u1ec7 Bailly v\u00e0 Lindelof m\u1eafc nhi\u1ec1u sai l\u1ea7m \u1edf tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u v\u1eeba qua</h3>\r\n            </td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n</h2>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">Eric Bailly \u0111\u00e3 t\u1ea1o ra m\u1ed9t trong nh\u1eefng m\u00e0n tr\u00ecnh di\u1ec5n t\u1ec7 nh\u1ea5t k\u1ec3 t\u1eeb khi kho\u00e1c \u00e1o Man United. Anh li\u00ean t\u1ee5c m\u1eafc sai l\u1ea7m c\u00e1 nh\u00e2n \u0111\u1ec3 Brighton c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 t\u1eadn d\u1ee5ng v\u00e0 ghi b\u00e0n.<br>\r\n<br>\r\nPha ph\u1ea1m l\u1ed7i ng\u1edb ng\u1ea9n c\u1ee7a Bailly v\u1edbi Pascal Gross \u0111\u00e3 khi\u1ebfn Qu\u1ef7 \u0111\u1ecf ph\u1ea3i h\u1ee9ng ch\u1ecbu m\u1ed9t qu\u1ea3 penalty, \u00edt ph\u00fat sau khi \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng \u0111ang c\u00f3 \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c s\u1ef1 h\u01b0ng ph\u1ea5n sau b\u00e0n g\u1ee1 c\u1ee7a Lukaku. S\u1ef1 m\u1ea5t t\u1eadp trung c\u1ee7a Bailly \u0111\u1ea7u hi\u1ec7p hai su\u00fdt khi\u1ebfn Man United b\u1ecb th\u1ee7ng l\u01b0\u1edbi th\u00eam m\u1ed9t b\u00e0n thua n\u1eefa. Nh\u1eefng pha ph\u00e1 b\u00f3ng c\u1ee7a c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 ng\u01b0\u1eddi B\u1edd Bi\u1ec3n Ng\u00e0 kh\u00e1 y\u1ebfu v\u00e0 kh\u00f4ng th\u1ec3 gi\u00fap Man United t\u1ed5 ch\u1ee9c ph\u1ea3n c\u00f4ng.<br>\r\n<br>\r\nNg\u01b0\u1eddi \u0111\u00e1 c\u1eb7p v\u1edbi Bailly l\u00e0 Lindelof c\u0169ng ch\u01a1i r\u1ea5t t\u1ec7 khi lu\u00f4n t\u1ea1o cho c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 \u0111\u1ed1i ph\u01b0\u01a1ng kh\u00f4ng gian v\u00e0 th\u1eddi gian \u0111\u1ec3 x\u1eed l\u00fd b\u00f3ng. C\u00e1ch m\u00e0 b\u1ed9 \u0111\u00f4i trung v\u1ec7 n\u00e0y \u0111\u1ec3 Glenn Murray c\u0169ng nh\u01b0 Pascal Gross tho\u00e1t xu\u1ed1ng g\u00e2y s\u00f3ng gi\u00f3 th\u1eadt s\u1ef1 qu\u00e1 nghi\u1ec7p d\u01b0. N\u1ebfu mu\u1ed1n chinh ph\u1ee5c ch\u1ee9c v\u00f4 \u0111\u1ecbch Premier League, \u0111i\u1ec1u quan tr\u1ecdng nh\u1ea5t l\u00e0 Man United c\u1ea7n ph\u1ea3i v\u00e1 ngay \u0111i\u1ec3m y\u1ebfu \u1edf h\u00e0ng ph\u00f2ng ng\u1ef1 hi\u1ec7n t\u1ea1i.</div>\r\n<h2>Anthony Martial\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width:100%; text-align: center;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"Martial\" title=\"Martial\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/8/20/104515-2.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td style=\"text-align: center\">\r\n            <h3>Martial ch\u01a1i kh\u00f4ng t\u1ed1t trong ng\u00e0y \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c l\u1ef1a ch\u1ecdn thay th\u1ebf Sanchez</h3>\r\n            </td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n</h2>\r\n</div><mobileadv><link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><div style=\"text-align: justify;\">V\u1edbi vi\u1ec7c Alexis Sanchez b\u1ea5t ng\u1edd b\u1ecb ch\u1ea5n th\u01b0\u01a1ng, Anthony Martial \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c trao c\u01a1 h\u1ed9i \u0111\u1ec3 ch\u1ee9ng t\u1ecf m\u00ecnh x\u1ee9ng \u0111\u00e1ng \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c ra s\u00e2n nhi\u1ec1u h\u01a1n. Nh\u01b0ng c\u0169ng gi\u1ed1ng nh\u01b0 nhi\u1ec1u c\u01a1 h\u1ed9i \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c trao tr\u01b0\u1edbc \u0111\u00f3, Martial \u0111\u00e3 kh\u00f4ng t\u1eadn d\u1ee5ng th\u00e0nh c\u00f4ng v\u00e0 c\u00f2n khi\u1ebfn kh\u1ea3 n\u0103ng ng\u1ed3i gh\u1ebf d\u1ef1 b\u1ecb c\u1ee7a anh tr\u1edf n\u00ean cao h\u01a1n nhi\u1ec1u.<br>\r\n<br>\r\nNgo\u00e0i m\u1ed9t pha \u0111\u1ed9t ph\u00e1 v\u00e0o v\u00f2ng c\u1ea5m \u0111\u1ed1i ph\u01b0\u01a1ng \u0111\u1ea7u tr\u1eadn, c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 ng\u01b0\u1eddi Ph\u00e1p kh\u00f4ng t\u1ea1o \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c m\u1ed1i \u0111e d\u1ecda n\u00e0o l\u00ean h\u00e0ng th\u1ee7 \u0111\u1ed1i ph\u01b0\u01a1ng. S\u1ef1 h\u1ed7 tr\u1ee3 h\u1eddi h\u1ee3t c\u1ee7a Shaw c\u0169ng khi\u1ebfn cho nh\u1eefng \u0111\u1ee3t l\u00ean b\u00f3ng c\u1ee7a Man \u0111\u1ecf \u1edf c\u00e1nh n\u00e0y t\u1ecf ra thi\u1ebfu hi\u1ec7u qu\u1ea3.<br>\r\n<br>\r\nKh\u1edfi \u0111\u1ea7u t\u1ec7 h\u1ea1i c\u1ee7a Martial \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c \u0111\u00e1nh d\u1ea5u b\u1eb1ng vi\u1ec7c b\u1ecb thay ra kh\u1ecfi s\u00e2n b\u1edfi Marouane Fellaini. V\u1edbi t\u00ecnh h\u00ecnh n\u00e0y, Sanchez ch\u1eb3ng ph\u1ea3i lo l\u1eafng g\u00ec nhi\u1ec1u v\u1ec1 vi\u1ec7c m\u1ea5t v\u1ecb tr\u00ed m\u1ed9t khi anh kh\u1ecfe m\u1ea1nh tr\u1edf l\u1ea1i.</div>\r\n<h2>Ashley Young\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width:100%; text-align: center;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"Young\" title=\"Young\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/8/20/104521-3.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td style=\"text-align: center\">\r\n            <h3>Young kh\u00f4ng th\u1eafng \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c c\u00e1c c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 \u0111\u1ed1i ph\u01b0\u01a1ng trong nh\u1eefng t\u00ecnh hu\u1ed1ng tranh ch\u1ea5p tay \u0111\u00f4i</h3>\r\n            </td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n</h2>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">C\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 ng\u01b0\u1eddi Anh \u0111\u00e3 c\u00f3 m\u1ed9t k\u1ef3 World Cup t\u1ea1m \u1ed5n t\u1ea1i Nga. Nh\u01b0ng m\u00e0n tr\u00ecnh di\u1ec5n tr\u01b0\u1edbc Brighton cho th\u1ea5y Young v\u1eabn ch\u01b0a c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 l\u1ef1c t\u1ed1t nh\u1ea5t \u0111\u1ec3 ra s\u00e2n thi \u0111\u1ea5u t\u1ea1i Premier League.<br>\r\n<br>\r\nL\u00e3o t\u01b0\u1edbng 33 tu\u1ed5i ph\u00f2ng ng\u1ef1 r\u1ea5t k\u00e9m. Anh li\u00ean t\u1ee5c \u0111\u1ec3 \u0111\u1ed1i th\u1ee7 t\u1ea1t b\u00f3ng th\u00e0nh c\u00f4ng t\u1eeb c\u00e1nh c\u1ee7a m\u00ecnh trong hi\u1ec7p m\u1ed9t. Khi l\u00ean tham gia t\u1ea5n c\u00f4ng, Young c\u0169ng kh\u00f4ng t\u1ea1t b\u00f3ng qua \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c s\u1ef1 truy c\u1ea3n c\u1ee7a h\u1eadu v\u1ec7 \u0111\u1ea7u ti\u00ean. Romelu Lukaku v\u00e0 Marouane Fellaini li\u00ean t\u1ee5c c\u00f3 m\u1eb7t \u0111\u00f3n b\u00f3ng \u1edf trong nh\u01b0ng nh\u1eefng qu\u1ea3 t\u1ea1t c\u1ee7a Young l\u1ea1i kh\u00f4ng \u0111\u1ea1t \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c \u0111\u1ed9 hi\u1ec7u qu\u1ea3 c\u1ea7n thi\u1ebft.<br>\r\n<br>\r\nNh\u00ecn chung, th\u1ec3 l\u1ef1c v\u00e0 s\u1ee9c b\u1ec1n c\u1ee7a Young l\u00fac n\u00e0y l\u00e0 ch\u01b0a \u0111\u1ee7 t\u1ed1t. N\u1ebfu Mourinho mu\u1ed1n s\u1eed d\u1ee5ng l\u00e3o t\u01b0\u1edbng ng\u01b0\u1eddi Anh, c\u00f3 l\u1ebd Qu\u1ef7 \u0111\u1ecf s\u1ebd ph\u1ea3i ch\u1ec9nh sang s\u01a1 \u0111\u1ed3 3 h\u1eadu v\u1ec7. \u0110\u00f3 c\u0169ng l\u00e0 c\u00e1ch t\u1ed1t nh\u1ea5t \u0111\u1ec3 gi\u1ea3i quy\u1ebft b\u00e0i to\u00e1n h\u00f3c b\u00faa \u1edf v\u1ecb tr\u00ed trung v\u1ec7 l\u00fac n\u00e0y.<br>\r\n<br>\r\n<strong>Xem th\u00eam nh\u1eefng tin t\u1ee9c kh\u00e1c sau tr\u1eadn Brighton 3-2&nbsp;MU:</strong><br>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelatepannel\">\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate\"><span href=\"/bong-da-anh/gary-neville-phat-bieu-ve-mu-172-194883.html\">Gary Neville ph\u00e1t bi\u1ec3u v\u1ec1 M.U</span></div>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate\"><span href=\"/bong-da-anh/anthony-martial-bi-chi-trich-du-doi-sau-tran-thua-brighton-172-194878.html\">Anthony Martial b\u1ecb ch\u1ec9 tr\u00edch d\u1eef d\u1ed9i sau tr\u1eadn thua Brighton</span></div>\r\n</div>\r\n<br>\r\n<br>\r\n<strong>Xu\u00e2n Phong (TTVN)</strong></div></div><advbottom>","new_url":"","id":"2561","checkdouble":"194886"},{"date":"11:19 20/08","title":"Gareth Bale n\u00f3i g\u00ec sau ng\u00e0y ra qu\u00e2n La Liga c\u1ee7a Real?","type":"B\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 Anh","img_url":"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/original/2018/8/20/gareth-bale-noi-gi-sau-ngay-ra-quan-la-liga-cua-real.jpg","new_desc":"<link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><h2>Gareth Bale ph\u00e1t bi\u1ec3u sau tr\u1eadn Real Madrid 2-0 Getafe. Tuy\u1ec3n th\u1ee7 x\u1ee9 Wales r\u1ea5t vui khi \u0111\u00f3ng g\u00f3p 1 b\u00e0n v\u00e0o chi\u1ebfn th\u1eafng c\u1ee7a Real ng\u00e0y ra qu\u00e2n t\u1ea1i La Liga.</h2><div style=\"text-align: justify;\">\u00a0</div>\r\n<h2 style=\"text-align: justify;\">Bale c\u1ea3m th\u1ea5y vui m\u1eebng</h2>\r\n</div><mobileadv><link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nNgay ph\u00fat 20 cu\u1ed9c ti\u1ebfp \u0111\u00f3n Getafe tr\u00ean s\u00e2n nh\u00e0 t\u1ea1i v\u00f2ng 1 La Liga 2018/19, Real Madrid \u0111\u00e3 c\u00f3 b\u00e0n m\u1edf t\u1ef7 s\u1ed1 do c\u00f4ng Dani Carvajal. T\u1edbi ph\u00fat 51, Gareth Bale \u1ea5n \u0111\u1ecbnh chi\u1ebfn th\u1eafng 2-0 cho \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng Ho\u00e0ng gia T\u00e2y Ban Nha.<br>\r\n<br>\r\nSau tr\u1eadn thua Atletico Madrid v\u1edbi t\u1ef7 s\u1ed1 4-2 \u1edf hi\u1ec7p ph\u1ee5 Si\u00eau c\u00fap ch\u00e2u \u00c2u, Real Madrid \u0111\u00e3 \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c c\u1ed5 v\u0169 b\u1eb1ng 3 \u0111i\u1ec3m tr\u1ecdn v\u1eb9n ng\u00e0y ra qu\u00e2n La Liga. Gareth Bale ph\u00e1t bi\u1ec3u sau tr\u1eadn Real Madrid 2-0 Getafe \u0111\u1ea7y ph\u1ea5n kh\u1edfi.<br>\r\n<br>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width:100%; text-align: center;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"Gareth Bale ph\u00e1t bi\u1ec3u sau tr\u1eadn Real Madrid 2-0 Getafe h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" title=\"Gareth Bale ph\u00e1t bi\u1ec3u sau tr\u1eadn Real Madrid 2-0 Getafe h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/8/20/gareth-bale-noi-gi-sau-ngay-ra-quan-la-liga-cua-real.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td style=\"text-align: center\">\r\n            <h3>Gareth Bale ph\u00e1t bi\u1ec3u sau tr\u1eadn Real Madrid 2-0 Getafe</h3>\r\n            </td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<br>\r\n\u201cT\u00f4i c\u1ea3m th\u1ea5y vui v\u00e0 d\u00f9 \u0111\u00e3 ghi b\u00e0n, \u0111i\u1ec1u quan tr\u1ecdng nh\u1ea5t l\u00e0 \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng gi\u00e0nh chi\u1ebfn th\u1eafng v\u00e0 ti\u1ebfp t\u1ee5c c\u1ea3i thi\u1ec7n s\u1ee9c m\u1ea1nh t\u1eadp th\u1ec3. M\u1ee5c ti\u00eau c\u1ee7a ch\u00fang t\u00f4i, gi\u1ed1ng nh\u01b0 m\u1ecdi n\u0103m, l\u00e0 v\u00f4 \u0111\u1ecbch t\u1ea5t c\u1ea3 c\u00e1c gi\u1ea3i \u0111\u1ea5u m\u00e0 m\u00ecnh tham gia.\u201d<br>\r\n<br>\r\n\u201cCh\u00fang t\u00f4i s\u1ebd c\u1ed1ng hi\u1ebfn h\u1ebft m\u00ecnh v\u00ec \u0111i\u1ec1u \u0111\u00f3. C\u00e1c t\u00e2n binh \u0111\u1ec1u \u0111\u00e3 c\u00f3 s\u1ef1 h\u00f2a nh\u1eadp r\u1ea5t nhanh. Ch\u00fang t\u00f4i \u0111\u00e3 gi\u00fap h\u1ecd b\u1eaft nh\u1ecbp \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c v\u1edbi l\u1ed1i ch\u01a1i chung v\u00e0 hy v\u1ecdng t\u1ea5t c\u1ea3 \u0111\u1ec1u s\u1ebd t\u1ecfa s\u00e1ng trong t\u01b0\u01a1ng lai g\u1ea7n.\u201d<br>\r\n\u00a0</div>\r\n<h2 style=\"text-align: justify;\">Nacho tin t\u01b0\u1edfng Bale</h2>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nSau s\u1ef1 ra \u0111i c\u1ee7a Cristiano Ronaldo, Gareth Bale l\u00e0 ng\u01b0\u1eddi \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c k\u1ef3 v\u1ecdng s\u1ebd \u0111\u1ee7 s\u1ee9c thay th\u1ebf cho ng\u01b0\u1eddi m\u1edbi chuy\u1ec3n t\u1edbi Juventus v\u1edbi gi\u00e1 112 tri\u1ec7u Euro t\u1ea1i Real Madrid. D\u00f9 v\u1eady, h\u1eadu v\u1ec7 Nacho Fernandez th\u00ec kh\u1eb3ng \u0111\u1ecbnh \u0111\u1ed3ng \u0111\u1ed9i Bale kh\u00f4ng c\u00f3 g\u00ec \u0111\u1ec3 ch\u1ee9ng minh v\u1edbi c\u00f4ng ch\u00fang.<br>\r\n<br>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelatepannel\">\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate2\"><span href=\"/truc-tiep-bong-da/real-madrid-vs-getafe-la-liga-2082018-372-194842.html\"><img src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/8/18/real-madrid-vs-getafe-la-liga-2082018.png\" alt=\"\"></span><span href=\"/truc-tiep-bong-da/real-madrid-vs-getafe-la-liga-2082018-372-194842.html\">Real Madrid 2-0 Getafe: Los Blancos th\u1eddi h\u1eadu Ronaldo kh\u1edfi \u0111\u1ea7u su\u00f4n s\u1ebb</span><br>\r\n<span>Tr\u00ean s\u00e2n nh\u00e0 Bernabeu, \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng Ho\u00e0ng gia TBN kh\u00f4ng m\u1ea5y kh\u00f3 kh\u0103n v\u00e0 v\u1ea5t v\u1ea3 \u0111\u1ec3 h\u1ea1 g\u1ee5c \u0111\u1ed1i th\u1ee7 \u0111\u1ea7u ti\u00ean t\u1ea1i La Liga 2018/19. Carvajal v\u00e0 Bale l\u00e0 hai c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 l\u1eadp...</span></div>\r\n</div>\r\n<br>\r\n\u201cC\u00e2u h\u1ecfi v\u1ec1 vai tr\u00f2 c\u1ee7a Gareth Bale sau s\u1ef1 ra \u0111i c\u1ee7a Ronaldo kh\u00f4ng n\u00ean \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c nh\u1eafc \u0111\u1ebfn\u201d, tuy\u1ec3n th\u1ee7 T\u00e2y Ban Nha n\u00f3i. \u201cRonaldo \u0111\u00e3 \u0111\u1ec3 l\u1ea1i d\u1ea5u \u1ea5n c\u1ee7a m\u00ecnh trong l\u1ecbch s\u1eed Real. C\u00f2n Bale l\u00e0 m\u1ed9t c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 th\u1ef1c s\u1ef1 quan tr\u1ecdng \u0111\u1ed1i v\u1edbi ch\u00fang t\u00f4i v\u00e0 \u0111\u00e3 gi\u00e0nh \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c nhi\u1ec1u danh hi\u1ec7u \u1edf \u0111\u00e2y. Anh \u1ea5y kh\u00f4ng c\u00f3 g\u00ec \u0111\u1ec3 ch\u1ee9ng minh cho b\u1ea5t c\u1ee9 ai.\u201d<br>\r\n<br>\r\n\u201cM\u1ecdi ng\u01b0\u1eddi \u0111\u1ec1u bi\u1ebft Real c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 tr\u00f4ng c\u1eady v\u00e0o Bale. T\u00f4i ch\u1eafc ch\u1eafn anh \u1ea5y s\u1ebd ti\u1ebfp t\u1ee5c ch\u01a1i t\u1ed1t. Ng\u01b0\u1eddi h\u00e2m m\u1ed9 \u1edf ph\u00eda sau Bale v\u00e0 anh \u1ea5y \u0111ang r\u1ea5t h\u1ea1nh ph\u00fac \u1edf CLB. Ch\u00fang t\u00f4i c\u00f3 nh\u1eefng m\u0169i c\u00f4ng tuy\u1ec7t v\u1eddi v\u00e0o l\u00fac n\u00e0y.\u201d<br>\r\n<br>\r\n<strong>Xem th\u00eam m\u1ed9t s\u1ed1 b\u00e0i vi\u1ebft kh\u00e1c v\u1ec1 Real Madrid tr\u00ean trang bongda24h.vn:<br>\r\n<br>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelatepannel\">\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate\"><span href=\"/bong-da-tbn/real-madrid-nang-gia-hoi-mua-cavani-len-63-trieu-bang-180-194880.html\">Real Madrid n\u00e2ng gi\u00e1 h\u1ecfi mua Cavani l\u00ean 63 tri\u1ec7u b\u1ea3ng</span></div>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate\"><span href=\"/bong-da-tbn/ra-quan-thang-loi-hlv-real-ca-ngoi-gareth-bale-180-194865.html\">Ra qu\u00e2n th\u1eafng l\u1ee3i, HLV Real ca ng\u1ee3i h\u1ecdc tr\u00f2</span></div>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate\"><span href=\"/bong-da-tbn/diem-nhan-real-madrid-20-getafe-los-blancos-van-khoe-thoi-hau-cr7-180-194863.html\">\u0110i\u1ec3m nh\u1ea5n Real Madrid 2-0 Getafe: Los Blancos v\u1eabn kh\u1ecfe th\u1eddi h\u1eadu CR7</span></div>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate\"><span href=\"/truc-tiep-bong-da/real-madrid-vs-getafe-la-liga-2082018-372-194842.html\">Real Madrid 2-0 Getafe: Los Blancos th\u1eddi h\u1eadu Ronaldo kh\u1edfi \u0111\u1ea7u su\u00f4n s\u1ebb</span></div>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate\"><span href=\"/video/clip-real-madrid-vs-getafe-20-highlights-la-liga-2018-328-194857.html\">Video t\u1ed5ng h\u1ee3p: Real Madrid 2-0 Getafe (V\u00f2ng 1 La Liga 2018/19)</span></div>\r\n</div>\r\n<br>\r\n<br>\r\nGia Vi (TTVN)<br>\r\n</strong></div></div><advbottom>","new_url":"","id":"2560","checkdouble":"194887"},{"date":"07:26 20/08","title":"L\u1ecbch thi \u0111\u1ea5u b\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 h\u00f4m nay (20/8/2018)","type":"B\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 Anh","img_url":"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/8/18/lich-thi-dau-bong-da-hom-nay-2082018.png","new_desc":"<link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7